citations:
    citation-asos-arya-iv:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Arya IV"
            text_from_source: "Neither wolves nor lions. Arya's skin prickled... Tom Sevenstrings rolled his eyes at that, but Harwin gave her an answer... Lord Beric moves about a lot, and seldom lets on what his plans are."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Arya travels with the Brotherhood Without Banners: Lem Lemoncloak, Tom Sevenstrings (Tom o' Sevens), Anguy, Greenbeard, Harwin, Jack-Be-Lucky. They search for Lord Beric Dondarrion. Visit Lady Smallwood of Acorn Hall. Gendry and Arya roughhouse. Brotherhood plans to ransom Arya to Robb at Riverrun."
